#############################################################################
#                                                                           #
#   KIRO-ISO  —  packages.x86_64                                        #
#                                                                           #
#   Organized into 3 risk tiers so it is clear what a user may safely       #
#   change without breaking the ISO build / boot / install.                 #
#                                                                           #
#     TIER 1  FROZEN ............ never remove (breaks build/boot/install)  #
#     TIER 2  KIRO CORE ......... change only if you know what you're doing #
#     TIER 3  USER-CHANGEABLE ... safe to add or remove freely              #
#                                                                           #
#   Within each tier packages are grouped by function. Commented (#) lines  #
#   are deliberately-disabled options kept for reference — uncomment to use.#
#                                                                           #
#############################################################################


#############################################################################
#  TIER 1 — FROZEN — DO NOT REMOVE                                          #
#  Removing any of these breaks the ISO build, the live boot, or Calamares. #
#############################################################################

