###  REPLACEMENT PRE-SEEDS — ship the post-rename package so the first
###  `pacman -Syu` has nothing to swap (no interactive replace prompt for users).
###  sdl2-compat Provides: sdl2; it is pulled in only transitively, so without this
###  line the old sdl2 installs and Arch's extra/sdl2-compat replaces it on first update.
sdl2-compat

