#############################################################################
#  EXTRA APPS — OPT-IN — NOT shipped by default                             #
#  Apps Kiro deliberately leaves off the base image. The kiro-iso-builder   #
#  "Add apps" page lists these; the build UNCOMMENTS the block(s) whose key #
#  is in build-scripts/package-additions.conf. Empty/missing file = add     #
#  nothing (= the standard production Kiro). Managed by build-the-iso.sh.    #
#  Block marker:  ### >>> EXTRA-APP <key> | <label> | <repo> >>>            #
#  Only list packages that resolve in an enabled build repo                 #
#  (core/extra/nemesis_repo/chaotic-aur/cachyos) — AUR/pip/npm will fail.   #
